# ---- Project data policy (load-bearing — read before "fixing") ----
# Raw datasets are NEVER committed; provenance + checksums are (see W1-01,
# data/DATA_PROVENANCE.md). Fixture excerpts live in tests/, not here.
data/raw/
data/*.csv
data/*.sqlite3
data/*.parquet

# NOTE: results/manifests/*.json are COMMITTED deliverables — deliberately NOT
# ignored. Every reported number traces to a manifest (config + seed + SHA);
# ignoring them would sever the provenance chain. Do not add them here.

# NOTE: uv.lock (arrives with W0-01) is COMMITTED — the lockfile is the
# dependency-level half of reproducibility. Do not add it here.
